      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Rights and status of frontier workers in the UK after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Frontier workers are EU, EEA and Swiss citizens who regularly commute to the UK because they are employed or self-employed here but live elsewhere. 
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

